snippet.title: Chris' Tutorials
snippet.description:
Quick computer tutorials based to help users with using various software. My typical topics include GIMP, DaVinci Resolve 17, Unity Engine, Unreal 4 Engine, Blender, and similar software.

For those planning to email me; Just as a heads up, i'm pretty bad about checking email so unless it's a question asked through my Udemy / Skillshare courses or Patreon there's a good chance I won't get back. It's just not time efficient for me to answer every question directly for free. Keep it short and simple if you can.
